<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="1237">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhang-san-64-57-35" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-san-64-57-35" class="zg-link" title="澹一">澹一</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$tu-zhe-chen" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/tu-zhe-chen" class="zg-link" title="涂哲琛">涂哲琛</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yu-ban-de-gu-tai" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yu-ban-de-gu-tai" class="zg-link" title="御坂的呱太">御坂的呱太</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3056885" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">1.<br>鼻炎是会呼吸的痛<br>它流在鼻涕中来回滚动<br>后悔补铁锌会痛<br>恨不东尼会痛<br>想闻不能闻最痛<br><br><br>2.<br>在山的那边，海的那边，有一座18号楼男生宿舍。<br>每天早上，我的床头都会多出一团纸，饱含着青春黏滑。<br><br><br>3.<br>清风恐成最大赢家。<br><br><br>4.<br>上网搜“过度手淫的危害”，完全一致，比如：<br><br>头发枯黄，没有光泽；<br>食欲不振，胃寒脾虚；<br>目光呆滞，视线模糊；<br>思维迟钝，记忆力差。<br><br><br>5.<br>常年捏鼻子，越长越像新疆人。<br><br><br>6.<br>记忆力差，有时候刚说完又说一遍。<br><br><br>7.<br>有些事我都已忘记<br>但我现在还记得<br>在一个下午，我的同学问我：“今天怎么不开心？”<br><br>“我鼻子不透气。”<br>“你怎么连话都说不清楚。”<br><br><br>8.<br>整天张着嘴，鼻子老出声，还要忍受旁人的嘲笑。<br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/88ab8df5942dae92aa2d3744ada5c801_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="359" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/88ab8df5942dae92aa2d3744ada5c801_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="359" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="600" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/88ab8df5942dae92aa2d3744ada5c801_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/88ab8df5942dae92aa2d3744ada5c801_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/e9da09f9d194f008c9e97b6d7932d92f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="333" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/e9da09f9d194f008c9e97b6d7932d92f_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="333" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/e9da09f9d194f008c9e97b6d7932d92f_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/e9da09f9d194f008c9e97b6d7932d92f_b.jpg"><br><noscript><img src="//pic3.zhimg.com/82581ac3fb5c6add082fc4ad85aab65e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="380" data-rawheight="306" class="content_image" width="380"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="380" data-rawheight="306" class="content_image lazy" width="380" data-actualsrc="//pic3.zhimg.com/82581ac3fb5c6add082fc4ad85aab65e_b.jpg"><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/45a20f64218432ce2f1887c258afa1db_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="268" data-rawheight="220" class="content_image" width="268"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="268" data-rawheight="220" class="content_image lazy" width="268" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/45a20f64218432ce2f1887c258afa1db_b.jpg"><br><br>9.<br>记忆力差，有时候刚说完又说一遍。<br><br>10.<br>每隔一段时间，会有那么几天量特别大。


</div>

